 {"id":"bd-3bxhj.3.7","title":"task(opentui-import IR): Build IR explainer tooling (graph dumps, provenance traces, pass diffs)","description":"Objective: Provide debuggability tools for developers/operators to inspect IR graphs, provenance slices, and before/after pass diffs.\\n\\nAcceptance criteria:\\n1. Explainer can emit human-readable and machine-readable outputs.\\n2. Pass diffs are stable and include semantic-change classification.\\n3. Tooling integrates with failure triage and certification reports.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:30:06.878083434Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:22.734035325Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["ir","opentui-import","tooling"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.7","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:30:06.878083434Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.7","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:21.806979840Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.7","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:22.273242266Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.7","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:22.733970103Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-3bxhj.3.8","title":"task(opentui-import IR tests): Unit tests for IR invariants, pass idempotence, and migration adapters","description":"Objective: Build unit and property tests covering schema validation, lowering correctness, normalization idempotence, inference sanity, and version migration safety.\\n\\nAcceptance criteria:\\n1. Randomized property tests enforce invariant preservation through pass pipeline.\\n2. Golden IR snapshots lock deterministic canonical output.\\n3. Failure logs include node IDs, pass name, invariant ID, and provenance pointers.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:31:00.448788760Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-24T22:20:06.334347612Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["ir","opentui-import","test","unit"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.8","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.1.6","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T22:20:06.334275147Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.8","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:31:00.448788760Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.8","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:23.182977323Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.8","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:23.848694423Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.8","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:24.305667045Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.8","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.6","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:24.770917966Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-3bxhj.3.9","title":"task(opentui-import IR tests): E2E ingestion-to-IR determinism script with stage-by-stage JSONL traces","description":"Objective: Implement end-to-end script that runs intake+analysis+IR pipeline over fixture corpus and verifies deterministic IR and artifact hashes across reruns.\\n\\nAcceptance criteria:\\n1. Script validates stage hashes and final IR hash consistency.\\n2. Supports deterministic replay mode with captured inputs and seeds.\\n3. Produces detailed JSONL traces and compact failure summaries for CI artifacts.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:31:05.376006780Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-24T22:20:12.219611708Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["e2e","ir","opentui-import","test"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.1.7","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T22:20:12.219553650Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.2.10","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:25.231982433Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:31:05.376006780Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.9","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:25.675663716Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-3bxhj.4","title":"epic(opentui-import): Translation engine and FrankenTUI code generation","description":"## Background\nTranslate canonical IR into idiomatic FrankenTUI code with high readability, predictable structure, and policy-aware fallback behavior.\n\n## Scope\n- Mapping atlas from IR constructs to FrankenTUI runtime/layout/widgets/style primitives.\n- Confidence-ranked planner selecting exact/approximate/extend-ftui strategies.\n- Code emission backend, project scaffolding, and optimization/readability passes.\n- Unit tests for planner/templates and E2E translate-build ledger pipelines.\n\n## Success Criteria\n1. Generated projects compile/run deterministically for supported migration profiles.\n2. Planner decisions are policy- and evidence-linked with explicit fallback semantics.\n3. Emitted code quality (structure/readability) meets formatter/lint and template invariants.\n4. Translate-and-build E2E scripts produce deterministic evidence ledgers.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:28:20.331961649Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-24T22:22:55.806108037Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["codegen","opentui-import","translation"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.4","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:28:20.331961649Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-3bxhj.4.1","title":"task(opentui-import translation): Build IR-to-FrankenTUI construct mapping atlas","description":"Objective: Define canonical mappings from IR constructs to FrankenTUI primitives (Model/update/view/subscriptions/layout/widgets/style/runtime APIs).\\n\\nAcceptance criteria:\\n1. Atlas references contract policy classes (exact/approx/extend/unsupported).\\n2. Mapping entries include preconditions, failure modes, and remediation strategy.\\n3. Atlas is versioned and consumed by planner and certification reporting.","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:31:37.318024984Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-25T05:58:05.520765049Z","closed_at":"2026-02-25T05:58:05.520746394Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["mapping","opentui-import","translation"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.1","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.1.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:26.130436618Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.1","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:26.591093061Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.1","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.4","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:31:37.318024984Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-3bxhj.4.10","title":"task(opentui-import translation tests): E2E translate-and-build script with detailed run ledger","description":"Objective: Implement end-to-end script that ingests fixture projects, runs full translation, builds generated FrankenTUI apps, and stores run ledgers with stage timings and hashes.\\n\\nAcceptance criteria:\\n1. Script supports batch fixture execution with deterministic ordering.\\n2. CI artifacts include generated source tarball, build logs, and JSONL stage ledger.\\n3. Failure output pinpoints failing stage and includes replay command.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:32:40.054812932Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-24T22:20:12.671391894Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["e2e","opentui-import","test","translation"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.10","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.1.7","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T22:20:12.671326993Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.10","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.3.9","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:35.773278282Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.10","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.4","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:32:40.054812932Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.10","depends_on_id":"bd-3bxhj.4.9","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:37:37.066956700Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
